Package javelin.controller.quality.resistance

Class EnergyResistance

  • java.lang.Object
    • javelin.controller.quality.Quality
      • javelin.controller.quality.resistance.EnergyResistance
  • public class EnergyResistance
extends Quality
    Tries to treat all energies as a single resistance. They should be .02CR but currently the game assume 1 point of energy resistance is actually 5 (one for each type of energy resistance).
    Author:
    alex
    See Also:
    ENERGYTYPES, Monster.energyresistance
